text: Cantharus vermeiji is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Pisaniidae, the true whelks. ==Description== ==Distribution== ==References== * Fraussen K. 2008. Cantharus vermeiji sp. nov., a new species from East Africa (Gastropoda: Buccinidae). Gloria Maris, 47(1-2): 24-29 ==External links== * Category:Pisaniidae Category:Gastropods described in 2008
title: Cantharus vermeiji
